  <data name="GralCallDescripton" xml:space="preserve">
    <value></value>
    <comment>Graldev is present in the world of Augmented Reality with the Gralcall project.&lt;br /&gt;
                 Gralcall is a web application initially born from a project in collaboration with our partner Associazione Manthano ETS.&lt;br /&gt;
                 We have in fact created a tourist and cultural itinerary to describe some Italian villages with the help of AR and informative videos.&lt;br /&gt;
                 Today Gralcall has evolved and is now a versatile and customizable tool for any need.&lt;br /&gt;
                 The areas of use of Gralcall range from tourism to catering, from advertising to gaming.&lt;br /&gt;
                 Contact us and we will offer you our support to realize your Augmented Reality project!&lt;br /&gt;</comment>
